---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---
<Base title="Stem Cell" description="A spec-driven app template. Define your data model and workflows in YAML, get a full-stack application.">
  <main class="flex min-h-[calc(100vh-4rem)] flex-col items-center justify-center px-6 py-24">

    <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-neutral-800 bg-neutral-900/60 px-4 py-1.5 text-xs font-medium text-neutral-400">
      <span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-green-400 animate-pulse"></span>
      Template Ready
    </div>

    <h1 class="mt-8 max-w-3xl text-center text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight sm:text-6xl lg:text-7xl">
      Stem Cell
    </h1>

    <p class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-xl text-center text-lg leading-relaxed text-neutral-400">
      A spec-driven app template. Edit two YAML files and get a
      Postgres-backed REST API, admin dashboard, and business workflows
      &mdash; no boilerplate.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-12 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4 sm:flex-row">
      <a href="/admin" class="rounded-xl bg-indigo-600 px-8 py-3.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-lg shadow-indigo-600/20 transition hover:bg-indigo-500 hover:shadow-indigo-500/30">
        Admin Dashboard
      </a>
      <a href="/api/docs" class="rounded-xl border border-neutral-700 px-8 py-3.5 text-sm font-medium text-neutral-300 transition hover:border-neutral-500 hover:text-white">
        API Documentation
      </a>
    </div>

    <section class="mx-auto mt-32 w-full max-w-5xl">
      <h2 class="text-center text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-neutral-500">
        How it works
      </h2>
      <div class="mt-10 grid gap-8 sm:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-neutral-800 bg-neutral-900/40 p-8 text-center">
          <div class="mx-auto mb-5 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-indigo-600/10 text-indigo-400">
            <svg class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M11 5H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v11a2 2 0 002 2h11a2 2 0 002-2v-5m-1.414-9.414a2 2 0 112.828 2.828L11.828 15H9v-2.828l8.586-8.586z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-100">Define your model</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-neutral-500">
            Edit <code class="text-neutral-400">specs/self.yaml</code> to declare entities, fields, and relations.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-neutral-800 bg-neutral-900/40 p-8 text-center">
          <div class="mx-auto mb-5 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-purple-600/10 text-purple-400">
            <svg class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 004.582 9m0 0H9m11 11v-5h-.581m0 0a8.003 8.003 0 01-15.357-2m15.357 2H15" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-100">Run codegen</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-neutral-500">
            <code class="text-neutral-400">mise run dev</code> generates migrations, API routes, and admin pages automatically.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-neutral-800 bg-neutral-900/40 p-8 text-center">
          <div class="mx-auto mb-5 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-pink-600/10 text-pink-400">
            <svg class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M5 3v4M3 5h4M6 17v4m-2-2h4m5-16l2.286 6.857L21 12l-5.714 2.143L13 21l-2.286-6.857L5 12l5.714-2.143L13 3z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-100">Ship it</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-neutral-500">
            Deploy with Docker or run directly. Your full-stack app is ready.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
</Base>
